biotools.summary:
Efficacy of WINROP as a Screening Tool for Retinopathy of Prematurity in the East Coast of Malaysia.

This online monitoring system, following weight gain, for predicting developing sight threatening ROP, was developed by the research group at The Sahlgrenska Center for Pediatric Ophthalmology Research.
